high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, take a right at the counter and walk to the table
Pick up the loaf of bread that is closest to you;  the loaf of bread that is to the right of the knife.
Turn around and walk to the counter in front of you, the turn left and head to the fridge on your left
Open the fridge and place the load of bread on the top shelf then close the fridge
turn left and cross the room, at the wall take a right and walk to the table. Turn right to face the table.
Pick up the load of bread that is sitting to the right of the kettle
Turn right and walk to the window, at the window turn left and head to the fridge that is on your left
Open the fridge and place the load of bread on the top shelf on the right of the bread that is already there then close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place loaves of bread in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the wall, then turn right to face the round table in the corner.
Pick up the loaf of bread closest to the chair with its back to the room.
Take the bread to the fridge to your right.
Place the loaf of bread in the center of the top fridge shelf, with the narrow end of the bread pointing toward you.
Turn to your left and go all the way back to the wall, then go to the right, between the wall and the round table and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the loaf of bread that is closest to the knife and spatula.
Return to the fridge.
Put the loaf on the top fridge shelf on the left, next to the other loaf.
anns.task_desc: Put two loaves of bread into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, go straight, then turn right to face the kitchen table
Pick up the loaf of bread below the tomato.
Turn around and make a left until you are in front of the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the loaf in the center of the top shelf, then close the door.
Walk back to the kitchen table.
pick up the loaf nearest to the spatula.
Walk back to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and place the loaf to the left of the other loaf.
anns.task_desc: Retrieve bread from the kitchen table and store them in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left, move past the counter on the left, turn right, move to the table
Pick up the nearest loaf of bread on the table
Turn around, move one floor tile, turn left, move to the fridge, turn left
Open the fridge, put the loaf on the center shelf, close the doors
Turn left, move to the wall, turn right, move to the chair, turn right
Pick up the loaf of bread on the table
Turn right, move to the window, turn left, move to the fridge, turn left
Open the fridge, place the loaf next to the other loaf, close the doors
anns.task_desc: Put two loaves of bread in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the fridge
Pick up bread from the table
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Put the bread inside the fridge and close the door
Move to the table to the left of the fridge
Pick up bread from the table
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Put the bread inside the fridge and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put two loaves of bread in the fridge.
